OL,3,CNorthern Ireland MPs call on Prime
OL,4,CMinister to act amid fuel protests
OL,6,FFarmers are warning that more protests
OL,7,Fover fuel prices and the cost of
OL,8,Fliving are to be expected across
OL,9,FNorthern Ireland.
OL,11,FSlow-moving convoys of tractors and
OL,12,Fother vehicles brought disruption to a
OL,13,Fnumber of major roads in Northern
OL,14,FIreland on Tuesday.
OL,16,FA number of people were given Fixed
OL,17,FPenalty Notices for driving offences.
OL,18,FOne farmer told UTV the protestors
OL,19,Ffelt they had "no choice".
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G1/13
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
