CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F448A1776359147
OL,3,CNorthern Ireland MPs call on Prime
OL,4,CMinister to act amid fuel protests
OL,6,FIt came after larger-scale fuel
OL,7,Fprotests in the Republic of Ireland,
OL,8,Fwhere motorways were brought to a
OL,9,Fstandstill and fuel depots blockaded.
OL,11,FBallygowan farmer, Sam Hanna is now
OL,12,Ffacing legal action after a protest in
OL,13,FBelfast.
OL,15,FSpeaking to UTV on Wednesday, he said:
OL,16,F"Last night, just after 8 o'clock, two
OL,17,Fpolice officers arrived at my door to
OL,18,Foffer me a summons, for court, or take
OL,19,Fthree points and a fine."
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/13
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,449,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44803
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F448A1776359147
OL,3,CNorthern Ireland MPs call on Prime
OL,4,CMinister to act amid fuel protests
OL,6,F"Other people might say you should
OL,7,Fhave known better, you shouldn't have
OL,8,Fbeen there, but at the same time,
OL,9,Fwe're trying to make a stand.
OL,11,F"It's a bit extortionate, the reaction
OL,12,Fto this.
OL,14,F"If we get a date for court, we're
OL,15,Fgoing to have to go and fight it, and
OL,16,FI would advise anybody else that gets
OL,17,Fa date for court too, we're going to
OL,18,Fhave to get together and go together."
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G3/13
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
