OL,3,CNorthern Ireland MPs call on Prime
OL,4,CMinister to act amid fuel protests
OL,6,FMeanwhile, Northern Ireland MPs have
OL,7,Fcalled on the Prime Minister to act
OL,8,Famid protests driven by rising energy
OL,9,Fbills.
OL,11,FSpeaking at Prime Minister's Questions
OL,12,Fon Wednesday, DUP MP Gregory Campbell
OL,13,Fwarned that more protests are being
OL,14,Forganised for next week, and that
OL,15,Faction is needed "to ensure these
OL,16,Fprotests don't escalate out of
OL,17,Fcontrol".
OL,26,@wD@ROUyD@HO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G4/13
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,449,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44805
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F448A1776359147
OL,3,CNorthern Ireland MPs call on Prime
OL,4,CMinister to act amid fuel protests
OL,6,FThe East Londonderry MP said: "Prime
OL,7,FMinister, there is severe hardship
OL,8,Fbeing experienced by businesses,
OL,9,Fconsumers and families right across
OL,10,Fthe United Kingdom.
OL,12,F"Not just normal cost-of-living costs,
OL,13,Fbut fuel costs are exceptionally high
OL,14,Fand getting higher.
OL,16,F"There are protests being organised as
OL,17,Fwe speak for next week.
OL,26,@nD@_OUtD@AOUxD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G5/13
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,449,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44806
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F448A1776359147
OL,3,CNorthern Ireland MPs call on Prime
OL,4,CMinister to act amid fuel protests
OL,6,F"Prime Minister, we need action
OL,7,Fdelivered as quickly as possible in
OL,8,Forder to ensure that these protests
OL,9,Fdon't escalate out of control and
OL,10,Fpeople see that politics matters,
OL,11,Fgovernments listen and take action,
OL,12,Frather than just offer words."
OL,14,FResponding, Sir Keir Starmer said: "I
OL,15,Fknow that his constituents and all of
OL,16,Fthose in Northern Ireland are
OL,17,Fconcerned about the impact that the
OL,18,Fwar in Iran is having on them.
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@^O]vD@dOU
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G6/13
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,449,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44807
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F448A1776359147
OL,3,CNorthern Ireland MPs call on Prime
OL,4,CMinister to act amid fuel protests
OL,6,F"I was in Northern Ireland just a few
OL,7,Fweeks ago, where I spoke directly to
OL,8,Fparty leaders and we announced what we
OL,9,Fdoing in that regard on heating oil.
OL,11,F"Obviously, fuel duty is frozen until
OL,12,FSeptember. Energy bills have been
OL,13,Freduced, and we have also made it
OL,14,Fclear that we wouldn't tolerate
OL,15,Fprofiteering or unfair practices,
OL,16,Fwhich was a particular concern raised
OL,17,Fwith me when I was over in Northern
OL,18,FIreland.
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G7/13
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,449,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44808
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F448A1776359147
OL,3,CNorthern Ireland MPs call on Prime
OL,4,CMinister to act amid fuel protests
OL,6,F"The most important thing we can do is
OL,7,Fto de-escalate the conflict and get
OL,8,Fthe Strait of Hormuz open, and that's
OL,9,Fwhy I'm co-hosting the summit on
OL,10,FFriday, in order to make progress on
OL,11,Fboth those fronts."
OL,13,FAlliance MP Sorcha Eastwood said her
OL,14,Fconstituents feel "let down" by the
OL,15,FGovernment, and urged ministers to
OL,16,F"change economic and fiscal course".
OL,18,FThe Lagan Valley MP told the Prime
OL,19,FMinister: "Two years ago, people voted
OL,20,Ffor change, but what have they got?
OL,21,FMore of the same.
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@SO]vD@SOUvD@\O]xD@AOUxD@cO]{D@
OL,26,AKOU
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G8/13
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,449,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44809
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F448A1776359147
OL,3,CNorthern Ireland MPs call on Prime
OL,4,CMinister to act amid fuel protests
OL,6,F"But it hasn't been them that have let
OL,7,Fdown their end of the bargain.
OL,9,F"My constituents are working
OL,10,Fthemselves to the bone, and let's be
OL,11,Fabsolutely clear, they are working and
OL,12,Fstill having to claim benefits.
OL,14,F"There's not a single section of
OL,15,Fsociety, whether it's farmers, care
OL,16,Fworkers, students, who haven't been
OL,17,Flet down. And I don't want that to be
OL,18,Fthe case.
OL,26,@nD@AOUqD@AOUvD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G9/13
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,449,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44810
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F448A1776359147
OL,3,CNorthern Ireland MPs call on Prime
OL,4,CMinister to act amid fuel protests
OL,6,F"We need to show that this House works
OL,7,Ffor them, because actors will step
OL,8,Finto that space.
OL,10,F"People would love nothing more than
OL,11,Ffor our democracy to be toppled
OL,12,Fbecause we cannot show our people a
OL,13,Fbetter way of life.
OL,15,F"We used to say to people: if you work
OL,16,Fhard, you get on in life. That hasn't
OL,17,Fbeen the case for years.
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@AOUwD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G10/13
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,449,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44811
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F448A1776359147
OL,3,CNorthern Ireland MPs call on Prime
OL,4,CMinister to act amid fuel protests
OL,6,F"Will this Government now change
OL,7,Feconomic and fiscal course and deliver
OL,8,Ffor people in the worst cost of living
OL,9,Fcrisis?"
OL,11,FSir Keir responded: "Wages are going
OL,12,Fup higher in the first year of this
OL,13,FLabour Government than they did in the
OL,14,F10 years of the party opposite being
OL,15,Fin power.
OL,17,F"We've taken the decision in the
OL,18,Fbudget to cut energy bills across the
OL,19,Fcountry.
OL,26,@nD@AOUqD@HO]sD@UOUyD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G11/13
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,449,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44812
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F448A1776359147
OL,3,CNorthern Ireland MPs call on Prime
OL,4,CMinister to act amid fuel protests
OL,6,F"I was in Northern Ireland, as she
OL,7,Fknows, just a few weeks ago, making
OL,8,Fthe announcement about heating oil,
OL,9,Fwhich is obviously a huge concern in
OL,10,FNorthern Ireland, hearing what people
OL,11,Fhad to say, putting in place #53
OL,12,Fmillion.
OL,14,F"The authorities in Northern Ireland
OL,15,Fwill administer that, but we're
OL,16,Flooking more widely at what we can do."
OL,18,FCatch up with the latest UTV Live on
OL,19,FITVX
